{"word":"G4181 - πολυμερῶς - polymerōs - pol-oo-mer'-oce - At sundry times","slug":"G4181","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πολυμερῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>polymerōs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pol-oo-mer'-oce"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>At sundry times"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;&#x03C2; - polumero&#x0304;s</b> - <i>pol-oo-mer'-oce</i><p/>Adverb from a compound of <a href=\"#/G4183\">G4183</a> and <a href=\"#/G3313\">G3313</a>; <i>in many portions</i>, that is, <i>variously</i> as to time and agency (<i>piecemeal</i>): - at sundry times."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4178\">G4178</a>, <a href=\"#/G4180\">G4180</a>, <a href=\"#/G4182\">G4182</a>, <a href=\"#/G4183\">G4183</a>"}]}